    <title>2018 08 17 OpenCV-Python教程(1)--&gt;安装与导入</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/08/17/2018-08-17-OpenCV-Python%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B-1-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/08/17/2018-08-17-OpenCV-Python教程-1-安装与导入/</id>
    <published>2018-08-17T09:33:56.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-08-17T10:34:25.626Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="OpenCV-Python教程-1-—-安装与导入"><a href="#OpenCV-Python教程-1-—-安装与导入" class="headerlink" title="OpenCV-Python教程(1) —- 安装与导入"></a>OpenCV-Python教程(1) —- 安装与导入</h2><ol><li>安装Anaconda</li></ol><ul><li>详细内容见<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/32925500" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Anaconda介绍、安装及使用教程</a></li><li>检查是否安装完成anaconda，在终端输入如下指令</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>会有如下输出，其中4.3.30表示anaconda的版本号</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda 4.3.30</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>创建新的OpenCV环境<br>Anaconda 创建新环境的语法如下：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda create --name &lt;env_name&gt; &lt;package_names&gt;</span><br><span class="line">@param: &lt;env_name&gt; 即创建的环境名。建议以英文命名，且不加空格。</span><br><span class="line">@param: &lt;package_names&gt; 即安装在环境中的包名。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>如果要安装指定的版本号，则只需要在包名后面以 = 和版本号的形式执行。如： conda create –name python2 python=2.7 ，即创建一个名为“python2”的环境，环境中安装版本为2.7的python。</li><li>如果要在新创建的环境中创建多个包，则直接在 &lt;package_names&gt; 后以空格隔开，添加多个包名即可。如： conda create -n python3 python=3.5 numpy pandas ，即创建一个名为“python3”的环境，环境中安装版本为3.5的python，同时也安装了numpy和pandas。</li><li>默认情况下，新创建的环境将会被保存在 /Users/&lt;user_name&gt;/anaconda3/env 目录下，其中， &lt;user_name&gt; 为当前用户的用户名。</li></ul><p>我们选择输入</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda create --name OpenCV python=3.5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>激活与退出OpenCV环境<br>想用环境里的包需要激活环境:</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> activate OpenCV</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在不需要用到环境时，退出环境：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> deactivate OpenCV</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li>安装OpenCV学习需要的库与包</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda install numpy tqdm scipy scikit-image</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是opencv的安装异常智障，经常会出现各种各样装好了但是无法import cv2的报错，所以经过长时间的验证，只有如下方法是有效的。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda install -c menpo opencv3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="5"><li>检查是否安装完成<br>激活环境后在终端输入</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>会有如下输出，意味着进入了python的交互，</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Python <span class="number">3.5</span><span class="number">.4</span> |Continuum Analytics, Inc.| (default, Aug <span class="number">14</span> <span class="number">2017</span>, <span class="number">12</span>:<span class="number">43</span>:<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line">[GCC <span class="number">4.2</span><span class="number">.1</span> Compatible Apple LLVM <span class="number">6.0</span> (clang<span class="number">-600.0</span><span class="number">.57</span>)] on darwin</span><br><span class="line">Type <span class="string">"help"</span>, <span class="string">"copyright"</span>, <span class="string">"credits"</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> <span class="string">"license"</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> more information.</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>检查之前的包是否安装成功，按照如下输入：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> cv2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> scipy</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> tqdm</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> skimage</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>正常的结果应该是和上面一模一样没有输出，代表着导入没有问题，否则导入的时候会有一大堆报错。</p>]]></content>
    
